+        ``timestamp``, ``session_id``, ``agent``, ``trigger``, ``model``,
+        ``provider``, ``tokens_before``, ``tokens_after``,
+        ``messages_in``, ``messages_out``, ``summary_file``,
+        ``preserved_task_ids``, ``preserved_user_prefs``,
+        ``preserved_open_blockers``, ``threshold_tokens``.
+        """
